#: 21337012-0-5261
msgctxt "21337012-0-5261"
msgid "By Sir Relequen, Wing Captain of the Welkynars"
"\n"
"\nThough the Knightly Order of the Welkynars numbers no more than four members at a time, each of those knights needs a broad array of equipment, including armor of all weights as well as a complete array of weapons. This gear must be made to exact specifications of the very best materials, adhering strictly to the guidelines stated below. Only equipment that is well and properly made will be accepted into the Welkynar Armory. "
"\n"
"\nSHIELDS"
"\n"
"\nThe Welkynar's shield, with its overlapping plumage rendered in carbon steel, brass, and copper, represents the inescapable wings of Elven justice and Altmeri martial prowess. Let evildoers who threaten Summerset beware! This land is under Welkynar protection."
msgstr "ウェルキナーのウィングキャプテン、レレクエン著\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナー騎士団の数が同時に4名を超えることはないが、各騎士には幅広い装備が必要となり、装備にはあらゆる重さの鎧と全ての武器種が含まれる。これらの装備は最高の材料を使い、精密な仕様に基づいて作られる。下記の指針には厳格に従うこと。ウェルキナーの武器庫が受け入れるのは、出来が良く適切に作られた装備のみである。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n盾\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n炭素鋼、真鍮、銅を重ねた羽根付きのウェルキナーの盾は、エルフの正義の逃れられぬ翼と、アルトマーの戦いに関する熟達を示す。サマーセットを脅かす悪人たちよ、気をつけることだ！ この地はウェルキナーの庇護にある。"

#: 51188213-0-5261
msgctxt "51188213-0-5261"
msgid "Crafting Motif 67: Welkynar Shields"
msgstr "クラフトモチーフ67: ウェルキナーの盾"

#: 21337012-0-5260
msgctxt "21337012-0-5260"
msgid "By Sir Relequen, Wing Captain of the Welkynars"
"\n"
"\nThough the Knightly Order of the Welkynars numbers no more than four members at a time, each of those knights needs a broad array of equipment, including armor of all weights as well as a complete array of weapons. This gear must be made to exact specifications of the very best materials, adhering strictly to the guidelines stated below. Only equipment that is well and properly made will be accepted into the Welkynar Armory. "
"\n"
"\nMACES"
"\n"
"\nWhen a Welkynar's mace strikes, with its heavy business end forged in the shape of four beaked gryphon heads, it's as if the entire Aerie of the Order smites its opponent at once! Though the gilded gryphon heads look delicate, they're actually crafted of carbon steel surrounding a solid lead core."
msgstr "ウェルキナーのウィングキャプテン、レレクエン著\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナー騎士団の数が同時に4名を超えることはないが、各騎士には幅広い装備が必要となり、装備にはあらゆる重さの鎧と全ての武器種が含まれる。これらの装備は最高の材料を使い、精密な仕様に基づいて作られる。下記の指針には厳格に従うこと。ウェルキナーの武器庫が受け入れるのは、出来が良く適切に作られた装備のみである。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n戦棍\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナーの戦棍の、嘴のついた4羽のグリフォンの頭の姿で鍛造された重いヘッドが命中すると、騎士団の高巣ごと敵を強打するような効果がある！ 金箔したグリフォンの頭は精巧に見えるが、実際には闇の炭素鋼が堅い鉛の核を覆っている。"

#: 51188213-0-5260
msgctxt "51188213-0-5260"
msgid "Crafting Motif 67: Welkynar Maces"
msgstr "クラフトモチーフ67: ウェルキナーの戦棍"

#: 21337012-0-5259
msgctxt "21337012-0-5259"
msgid "By Sir Relequen, Wing Captain of the Welkynars"
"\n"
"\nThough the Knightly Order of the Welkynars numbers no more than four members at a time, each of those knights needs a broad array of equipment, including armor of all weights as well as a complete array of weapons. This gear must be made to exact specifications of the very best materials, adhering strictly to the guidelines stated below. Only equipment that is well and properly made will be accepted into the Welkynar Armory. "
"\n"
"\nLEG GREAVES"
"\n"
"\nOur resplendent metal poleyns, adorned with gilded wing symbols, certainly draw attention from the rest of our leg armor, cuisses that are functional though less spectacular than our knee bosses. Welkynar greaves consist of light overlapping plates backed by flexible flaxen fabric."
msgstr "ウェルキナーのウィングキャプテン、レレクエン著\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナー騎士団の数が同時に4名を超えることはないが、各騎士には幅広い装備が必要となり、装備にはあらゆる重さの鎧と全ての武器種が含まれる。これらの装備は最高の材料を使い、精密な仕様に基づいて作られる。下記の指針には厳格に従うこと。ウェルキナーの武器庫が受け入れるのは、出来が良く適切に作られた装備のみである。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n脚当て\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我々の輝く金属の膝当てには金箔した翼の象徴が飾られ、機能的だが我々のものより見栄えに劣る他の脚当てより、明らかに注目を引く。ウェルキナーのグリーヴは柔軟な亜麻の織物が支える、軽量の板を重ねている。"

#: 51188213-0-5259
msgctxt "51188213-0-5259"
msgid "Crafting Motif 67: Welkynar Legs"
msgstr "クラフトモチーフ67: ウェルキナーの脚当て"

#: 21337012-0-5258
msgctxt "21337012-0-5258"
msgid "By Sir Relequen, Wing Captain of the Welkynars"
"\n"
"\nThough the Knightly Order of the Welkynars numbers no more than four members at a time, each of those knights needs a broad array of equipment, including armor of all weights as well as a complete array of weapons. This gear must be made to exact specifications of the very best materials, adhering strictly to the guidelines stated below. Only equipment that is well and properly made will be accepted into the Welkynar Armory. "
"\n"
"\nHELMETS"
"\n"
"\nOur helmets have been rightly described as "magnificent confections of plumes and gilt," with avian motifs such as cheek pieces that resemble gryphon wings, and a forepeak like a gryphon's pointed bill. They were designed by Mornyalemar the Battle-Hardy generations ago, and we see no reason to change them now."
msgstr "ウェルキナーのウィングキャプテン、レレクエン著\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナー騎士団の数が同時に4名を超えることはないが、各騎士には幅広い装備が必要となり、装備にはあらゆる重さの鎧と全ての武器種が含まれる。これらの装備は最高の材料を使い、精密な仕様に基づいて作られる。下記の指針には厳格に従うこと。ウェルキナーの武器庫が受け入れるのは、出来が良く適切に作られた装備のみである。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n兜\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我々の兜は「羽根と金箔の壮麗なる混合」であると適切に表現されており、グリフォンの翼に似た側部、グリフォンの尖った嘴のような前面など、鳥をモチーフにしている。これらは数世代前に歴戦の戦士モーニャレマーが設計し、現在も変更する理由はない。"

#: 51188213-0-5258
msgctxt "51188213-0-5258"
msgid "Crafting Motif 67: Welkynar Helmets"
msgstr "クラフトモチーフ67: ウェルキナーの兜"

#: 21337012-0-5257
msgctxt "21337012-0-5257"
msgid "By Sir Relequen, Wing Captain of the Welkynars"
"\n"
"\nThough the Knightly Order of the Welkynars numbers no more than four members at a time, each of those knights needs a broad array of equipment, including armor of all weights as well as a complete array of weapons. This gear must be made to exact specifications of the very best materials, adhering strictly to the guidelines stated below. Only equipment that is well and properly made will be accepted into the Welkynar Armory. "
"\n"
"\nGLOVES"
"\n"
"\nA Welkynar's substantial but intricate gauntlets may be the knight's proudest belongings, since they are among the first items of gear issued to a squire-in-training. If you give any thought to the practical issues of training spirited gryphon mounts, with their powerful, snapping beaks, you'll understand the need for sturdy gauntlets and vambraces!"
msgstr "ウェルキナーのウィングキャプテン、レレクエン著\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナー騎士団の数が同時に4名を超えることはないが、各騎士には幅広い装備が必要となり、装備にはあらゆる重さの鎧と全ての武器種が含まれる。これらの装備は最高の材料を使い、精密な仕様に基づいて作られる。下記の指針には厳格に従うこと。ウェルキナーの武器庫が受け入れるのは、出来が良く適切に作られた装備のみである。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n手袋\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナーの丈夫ではあるが精妙な篭手は、騎士が最も誇りに思う品かもしれない。訓練中の騎士の従者に初期から支給されるためだ。強力で音を立てる嘴のついた、元気のよいグリフォンを騎乗動物とする訓練について、現実的な問題を考えてみよう。頑丈な篭手と腕当てが必要な理由は理解できるはずだ！"

#: 51188213-0-5257
msgctxt "51188213-0-5257"
msgid "Crafting Motif 67: Welkynar Gloves"
msgstr "クラフトモチーフ67: ウェルキナーの手袋"

#: 21337012-0-5256
msgctxt "21337012-0-5256"
msgid "By Sir Relequen, Wing Captain of the Welkynars"
"\n"
"\nThough the Knightly Order of the Welkynars numbers no more than four members at a time, each of those knights needs a broad array of equipment, including armor of all weights as well as a complete array of weapons. This gear must be made to exact specifications of the very best materials, adhering strictly to the guidelines stated below. Only equipment that is well and properly made will be accepted into the Welkynar Armory. "
"\n"
"\nDAGGERS"
"\n"
"\nA Welkynar's dagger is made of dark carbon steel and is doubly edged, but it's really a punching dagger so it's the needle-sharp point that counts.  The crossguard evokes gryphon wings, forged thicker and more solid than they appear to enable the dagger to be used as a parrying weapon."
msgstr "ウェルキナーのウィングキャプテン、レレクエン著\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナー騎士団の数が同時に4名を超えることはないが、各騎士には幅広い装備が必要となり、装備にはあらゆる重さの鎧と全ての武器種が含まれる。これらの装備は最高の材料を使い、精密な仕様に基づいて作られる。下記の指針には厳格に従うこと。ウェルキナーの武器庫が受け入れるのは、出来が良く適切に作られた装備のみである。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n短剣\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nウェルキナーの短剣は闇の炭素鋼製で、諸刃だが実際には刺突用の短剣であるため、重要なのは非常に鋭い先端である。クロスガードはグリフォンの翼を想起させ、見た目より厚く堅く鍛造されており、受け流し用の武器としても使える。"

#: 51188213-0-5256
msgctxt "51188213-0-5256"
msgid "Crafting Motif 67: Welkynar Daggers"
msgstr "クラフトモチーフ67: ウェルキナーの短剣"

#: 21337012-0-5255
