#: 21337012-0-4942
msgctxt "21337012-0-4942"
msgid "By the Worm of Songs"
"\n"
"\nIn death is life, reanimation"
"\nA sacred and a dark vocation"
"\nOur Order's garb all shall recall"
"\nTheir final sight before they fall "
"\n"
"\nAXES"
"\n"
"\nWorm axe blade's like a severed ear"
"\nRestored to life as metal hacker"
"\nA mighty arm that all must fear"
"\nGlint of steel and gleam of lacquer"
"\n"
"\nBELTS"
"\n"
"\nEchoes of Coldharbour see"
"\nIn cinctures, sashes, belts"
"\nOn each hip are tassets three"
"\nWith hooks for scalps or pelts"
"\n"
"\nBOOTS"
"\n"
"\nEach sabaton is lapping, plated"
"\nLike those of Bal's dark legions"
"\nOur troops' corpses reanimated"
"\nReturned from deathly regions"
"\n"
"\nBOWS"
"\n"
"\nFrom bones defleshed we craft our bows"
"\nThey loose with bony rattle"
"\nThe skeletal dart Worm archer throws"
"\nSlays men like so much cattle "
"\n"
"\nCHEST PIECES"
"\n"
"\nWorm armor's plates are tributes all "
"\nTo our Lord of the Undead"
"\nThe skin and form of Molag Bal"
"\nTo steel and iron wed"
"\n"
"\nDAGGERS"
"\n"
"\nLike jagged fangs, our daggers curve"
"\nSerrated edge and point"
"\nGrim armaments, they also serve "
"\nTo sever and disjoint  "
"\n"
"\nGLOVES"
"\n"
"\nOur gauntlets guard forearms and hands"
"\nEnabling fists to grip"
"\nWith fingers clad in bony bands"
"\nEnsuring hafts don't slip"
"\n"
"\nHELMETS"
"\n"
"\nLike metal skull of Daedric beast"
"\nWorm helm enwraps your head"
"\nOverlapping, layered, creased"
"\nMarch leading our undead"
"\n"
"\nLEG GREAVES"
"\n"
"\nChausses echo chest design"
"\nColdharbour inspiration"
"\nDaedric chevron, curving line"
"\nOf Lord of Domination"
"\n"
"\nMACES"
"\n"
"\nWhen slaying foes to animate"
"\nThe mace has many charms"
"\nWe want a corpse in wholesome state"
"\nWith all its legs and arms"
"\n"
"\nSHIELDS"
"\n"
"\nOn Worm Cult shield the horns of Bal"
"\nAdorn o'erlapping plates"
"\nFor undeath is the fate of all"
"\nWho pass Coldharbour's gates "
"\n"
"\nSHOULDER ARMOR"
"\n"
"\nPauldrons sharp as fangéd skulls"
"\nAdorn Worm Cultists' shoulders"
"\nMortals rise as Black Worm thralls"
"\nOr in their graves shall molder "
"\n"
"\nSTAVES"
"\n"
"\nWith spellstaff horned like Bal himself"
"\nDark mages focus magic"
"\nThus mortals—human, beast, or Elf"
"\nAll meet their endings tragic    "
"\n"
"\nSWORDS"
"\n"
"\nSwords serrated, pointed, edged"
"\nTo twist in mortals' entrails"
"\nMarch forth, Worm Cultist fully-fledged"
"\nCause adversaries' wails"
msgstr "虫の歌より\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n死の中にある生と復活\\r"
"\n神聖なる暗黒の使命\\r"
"\n思い出させる教団の服\\r"
"\n倒れる前の最後の光景\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n斧\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n虫の斧の刃は切断された耳\\r"
"\n金属を切りに再び得た命\\r"
"\n誰もが恐れる強力な武器\\r"
"\n鋼の閃光と漆の輝き\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nベルト\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nコールドハーバーの残響は見ゆ\\r"
"\n帯、サッシュ、ベルトの中\\r"
"\n腰の上にはタセット3つ\\r"
"\n頭や生皮を下げるフックの下\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nブーツ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nメッキのサバトンは包む\\r"
"\nバルの暗黒の軍団を\\r"
"\n死体の部隊は蘇らせる\\r"
"\n死の領域より戻りし者を\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n弓\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n肉体の骨で弓を作る\\r"
"\n乾いた音を立てて骨は外れる\\r"
"\n虫の弓兵が骨の矢を放ち\\r"
"\n人を家畜のように倒し\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n胸当て\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n虫の鎧のプレートは捧げもの\\r"
"\n我らがアンデッドの王へ\\r"
"\n鋼と鉄を結ぶもの\\r"
"\nモラグ・バルの皮と姿へ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n短剣\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n曲がった短剣は牙のように波打つ\\r"
"\n鋸歯の刃と先端\\r"
"\n残忍な武器も役立つ\\r"
"\n解体と切断\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n手袋\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n篭手は前腕と手を守る\\r"
"\n拳を握れるようにしながら\\r"
"\n骨のバンドは指を守る\\r"
"\n柄が滑らぬようにしながら\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n兜\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nデイドラの獣の金属の頭蓋骨のように\\r"
"\n虫の兜は頭を包む\\r"
"\n重なり、重ね、疲れ果てたように\\r"
"\n行進はアンデッドを導く\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n脚当て\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nシャッセは胸と変わらず\\r"
"\nコールドハーバーの風体に\\r"
"\nデイドラのシェブロンは湾曲する\\r"
"\n支配の王の姿に\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n戦槌\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n敵を殺戮し蘇らせる時\\r"
"\n戦棍には利点が多くある\\r"
"\n完全な死体を望む時\\r"
"\n欠けぬ足と腕が得られる\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n盾\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n重なるプレートで飾れば\\r"
"\n虫の教団の盾にバルの角\\r"
"\nコールドハーバーの門を通れば\\r"
"\n不死の宿命に導かれるのは全ての者\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n肩防具\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n鋭きポールドロンは牙の頭蓋\\r"
"\n虫の教団の信者の肩を飾る\\r"
"\n定命の者は黒き虫の教団の奴隷\\r"
"\nでなくば墓の中で朽ちる\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n杖\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nバルのような角の呪文杖で\\r"
"\n闇の魔術師は魔力を集め\\r"
"\n人間、獣、エルフは全て\\r"
"\n最後に悲劇を迎え\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n剣\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n鋸歯で尖った鋭き剣を持て\\r"
"\n定命の者の腸を抉れ\\r"
"\n完全なる虫の教団の信者よ進め\\r"
"\n敵の慟哭を呼び起こせ"

