"\n"
"\nLEG GREAVES"
"\n"
"\nOverlapping plates protect the front of a mercenary's legs, with flexible leather at the back. The poleyn that protects the knee often features a vertical spike that echoes the "horn" on the helmet."
msgstr "ガスパール・ストーカーズ隊長、ガスパール・エスムリー著\\r"
